```json

  "text": "Amar aur Akhil sabse achhe dost the. Woh Indonesian jungle ke dil mein ek hi chote se gaon mein saath bade hue the. Gehri banyan ki jaron ki tarah, ladkon ke paas kai same khwabon aur tamanna'at thi.

Ek din, subah ka suraj khoobsurat aur roshan nikla. Ladke apni nayi kharidi hui boats aur nets ke saath machli pakadne ke liye nikle, ek zabardast din ki umeed mein. Lekin nikalne ke thodi der baad, ek tsunami horizon par garja, samundar aur sahil ko apne toofani gusse mein duba diya.

Ladke tumultuous paani se alag ho gaye aur beh gaye. Jaldi hi woh alag beaches par, apne gaon se miles door, pareshan, zakhmi aur pite hue jaghe.

Agarcheh dono ne saath mein chillaya, unki awazein samundar ki hulchul mein kho gayin. Woh alag ho gaye the, lekin ladke abhi bhi disaster ke baad mein dobara milne ki umeed rakhe hue the."
}
```

```json
{
  "text": "Volunteering abroad aik aisi cheez hai jis par zyada logon ko ghaur karna chahiye agar woh duniya mein farq laane ka meaningful tareeka dhund rahe hain. Yeh firsthand experience hasil karne, nayi culture explore karne, aur naye logon se milne ka unique tareeka hai. Lekin international volunteering ka aik faida jo aksar nazar andaz hota hai woh hai lasting, global impact banane ki potential.

Kayi salon se, volunteering abroad ka idea us clichÃ© se juda raha hai jis mein idealistic, college-aged students "make a difference" karne ki koshish karte hain developing countries mein. Halanke volunteering abroad ka matlab ab bhi local community ke saath important initiatives par kaam karna ho sakta hai taake logon ki zindagi behtar ho, ab aisi variety ke programs hain jo logon ko variety ke initiatives pursue karne ki ijazat dete hainâ€”medical, educational, environmental, aur zyadaâ€”subtler, aksar zyada successful tariqon se.

International volunteering projects developing countries mein invaluable hain jahan resources limited hain aur locals innovation use kar rahe hain farq laane ke liye. Kayi volunteers sustainable projects banane mein kamyab hote hain community ke input, needs, aur abilities par emphasis ke saath. Yeh projects outside knowledge aur expertise ke influx ki ijazat dete hain aise tareeke se jo traditional aid practices ke zariye explain nahi ho sakta.

Aksar yeh socha jata hai ke volunteering abroad bohot expensive ya unsafe hai kisi ke liye participate karne ke liye. Websites jaise ke Global Volunteers volunteers ke liye important resources provide karte hain jo abroad kaam karne ke liye willing hain, jis mein destination safety ke bare mein information, fundraising advice, aur project tracking shamil hai.

Din ke ant mein, international volunteerism volunteers aur communities dono ko incredible value provide karta hai jinki woh service karte hain. Volunteering abroad volunteers ko seekhne, doosron ki madad karne, aur nayi culture explore karne ka mauka deta hai incredibly hands-on tareeke se. Saath hi saath, volunteer projects lambe distances travel karte hain, communities ko dikhate hain ke doosre countries ke log unki situation ke bare mein care karte hain, aur valuable skills aur resources tak access provide karte hain."
}
```
